T1  - HOUSING MARKET DISCOUNT RATES: EVIDENCE FROM BARGAINING AND BIDDING WARS
AU  - Koster, Hans R.A.
AU  - Rouwendal, Jan
Y1  - 2024/05/01
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12679
T2  - International Economic Review
